ITEM.SQL: SELECT CANCEL_ID, DELETED_FLAG, CANCEL_INFO_OFFER_TYPE, CANCEL_INFO_OFFER_ID, DATE_UPDATED, DATE_CREATED, OFFER_ID FROM booker.aa_cancel_info_offer_pst WHERE CANCEL_INFO_OFFER_ID IN(1078,1067,1068,1069,1071,1072,1073,1079,1080,1074,1075,1076,1077,1070,1081) ORDER BY CANCEL_ID, DELETED_FLAG, CANCEL_INFO_OFFER_TYPE, CANCEL_INFO_OFFER_ID, DATE_UPDATED, DATE_CREATED, OFFER_ID

SELECT cancel_id, customer_id, subscription_id, plan_asin, cancel_date, cancel_type, cancel_conf_number, cancel_code, survey_rating, survey_comment,deleted_flag, date_updated,DATE_CREATED, fulfilled_flag, version, subs_plan_selection_id, future_cancellation FROM booker.aa_memb_cancel_information_pst where CANCEL_ID IN(40069501,40069503,40069504,40069505,40069506,40069507,40069500,40069510,40069502,40069508,40069509,40069499) order by cancel_id, customer_id, subscription_id, plan_asin, cancel_date, cancel_type, cancel_conf_number, cancel_code, survey_rating, survey_comment, deleted_flag, date_updated,DATE_CREATED, fulfilled_flag, version, subs_plan_selection_id, future_cancellation

SELECT offer_id, offer_type, offer_name, offer_value,date_created, date_updated, offer_description, marketplace_id, deleted_flag, offer_quantity, promotion_id FROM booker.aa_memb_cancel_offers_pst where offer_id IN(12,13,16,17,18,19,21,22,23,24,26,27) order by offer_id, offer_type, offer_name, offer_value,date_created, date_updated, offer_description, marketplace_id, deleted_flag, offer_quantity, promotion_id

SELECT membership_hiatus_id, subscription_id, plan_id, start_date, end_date, deleted_flag, date_updated, customer_id, expected_hiatus_end_date FROM booker.aa_membership_hiatus_pst WHERE membership_hiatus_id IN(169,173,174,180,181,182,183,184,185,186,187,188,189,190,191,192) ORDER BY membership_hiatus_id, subscription_id, plan_id, start_date, end_date, deleted_flag, date_updated, customer_id, expected_hiatus_end_date

SELECT credit_type, credit_type_description, restricted_product_type, restricted_category, restricted_provider, promotion_id, date_updated FROM booker.aa_memb_credit_type_pst WHERE credit_type IN(1,2,3,4,5,6,7) order by credit_type, credit_type_description, restricted_product_type, restricted_category, restricted_provider, promotion_id, date_updated
SELECT type_name, int_code, value, date_updated, DATE_CREATED FROM booker.aa_memb_enum_values_pst WHERE int_code IN(1,2,3,4,5,6) order by type_name, int_code, value, date_updated, DATE_CREATED

SELECT switch_rule_id, from_asin, to_asin, is_allowed, deleted_flag, date_updated, is_csc_rule, is_downgrade, bill_next_cycle, hide_display, display_order, marketplace_id FROM booker.aa_memb_switch_rule_pst where switch_rule_id IN(2275,2276,2277,2278,2279) order by switch_rule_id, from_asin, to_asin, is_allowed, deleted_flag, date_updated, is_csc_rule, is_downgrade, bill_next_cycle, hide_display, display_order, marketplace_id

select MRPI_ACTIVE_SEQ_NO, ORDER_ID, ITEM_NUMBER, CONSUMED_CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_USED, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, DATE_CREATED,CREDIT_VALUE_CONSUMED, REV_AMOUNT_CONSUMED from booker.AA_MRPI_ACTIVE_CREDIT_PST where MRPI_ACTIVE_SEQ_NO IN(24275,24274,23260,23259) order by MRPI_ACTIVE_SEQ_NO, ORDER_ID, ITEM_NUMBER, CONSUMED_CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_USED, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, DATE_CREATED,CREDIT_VALUE_CONSUMED, REV_AMOUNT_CONSUMED

SELECT MRPI_CONSUMED_SEQ_NO, ORDER_ID, ITEM_NUMBER, CONSUMED_CREDIT_SEQ_NO, CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_USED, DATE_UPDATED FROM booker.AA_MRPI_CONSUMED_CREDIT_PST WHERE MRPI_CONSUMED_SEQ_NO IN(120000019,120000021,120000020) order by MRPI_CONSUMED_SEQ_NO, ORDER_ID, ITEM_NUMBER, CONSUMED_CREDIT_SEQ_NO, CREDIT_ID, CREDIT_USED, DATE_UPDATED

select ITEM_SEQ, CURRENT_SUBSCRIPTION_ID, ACTION_CODE, ORDER_DATE, CUST_ID, DATE_UPDATED, MARKETPLACE_ID, CURRENT_SUBS_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, SUBS_TRANSACTION_GUID, PLAN_ID, SESSION_ID, USER_AGENT, PLATFORM, APPLICATION from booker.SUBSCRIPTION_ACTION_CODES_PST where ITEM_SEQ in(16696,17209,17215,17226,17238,17249,17210,17212,17213,17216,17203,17225) ORDER BY ITEM_SEQ, CURRENT_SUBSCRIPTION_ID, ACTION_CODE, ORDER_DATE, CUST_ID, DATE_UPDATED, MARKETPLACE_ID, CURRENT_SUBS_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, SUBS_TRANSACTION_GUID, PLAN_ID, SESSION_ID, USER_AGENT, PLATFORM, APPLICATION

SELECT SUBS_TRANS_GUID, AUD_SCHEDULE_ITEM_ID, CHARGE_TYPE, PLAN_SELECTION_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED FROM booker.SUBS_TRANS_SCHDL_ITEM_PST where SUBS_TRANS_GUID IN('1DQNMF7AGEWC098NQ500','Z47MY9RGEH2CDVG9WGG1','NMMKFD82GQMC9DFEP7D1','S1CY2PZMTVVJDF0TA881') ORDER BY SUBS_TRANS_GUID, AUD_SCHEDULE_ITEM_ID, CHARGE_TYPE, PLAN_SELECTION_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED

SELECT CREDIT_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, IS_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT, CREDIT_TYPE, CREDIT_STATUS, DATE_UPDATED, REV_AMOUNT, START_DATE, END_DATE, MEMBERSHIP_PLAN_ID, CREATE_REASON, CREDIT_ORDER_NUMBER, CREDIT_CREATED_DATE, CREDIT_UPDATED_DATE, CREDIT_GIFT_SEQ_ID, ISSUE_PLAN_ID, REPL_CRD_FLAG, ORIG_CRD_CONS_CREDIT_ID, REPL_CRD_ORD_NUMBER, REPL_CRD_ITEM_NUMBER, CREDIT_ORIG_ORDER_NUM, CREDIT_ORIG_ITEM_NUM, PROMOTION_ID, VERSION, DELETED_FLAG, NUM_PRODUCTS_ALLOWED, CART_ITEM_ID, ISSUE_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, MARKETPLACE_ID, CREDIT_VALUE, SOURCE, ORIG_REV_AMOUNT, CREDIT_VALUE_REMAINING /*, ORDER_ID, FULFILLMENT_TYPE*/ FROM booker.AA_USER_ACTIVE_CREDIT_PST where CREDIT_ID IN (158216164,158216165,158216166,158216167,158216169,158216173,158216176,158216177,158216178,158216179,158216180,158216181,158216182,158216183,158216184,158216185,158216186,158216187,158216188,158216192,158216193,158216194,158216168,158216170,158216171,158216172,158216174,158216175,158216162,158216163,158216189,158216190,158216191) ORDER BY CREDIT_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, IS_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT, CREDIT_TYPE, CREDIT_STATUS, DATE_UPDATED, REV_AMOUNT, START_DATE, END_DATE, MEMBERSHIP_PLAN_ID, CREATE_REASON, CREDIT_ORDER_NUMBER, CREDIT_CREATED_DATE, CREDIT_UPDATED_DATE, CREDIT_GIFT_SEQ_ID, ISSUE_PLAN_ID, REPL_CRD_FLAG, ORIG_CRD_CONS_CREDIT_ID, REPL_CRD_ORD_NUMBER, REPL_CRD_ITEM_NUMBER, CREDIT_ORIG_ORDER_NUM, CREDIT_ORIG_ITEM_NUM, PROMOTION_ID, VERSION, DELETED_FLAG, NUM_PRODUCTS_ALLOWED, CART_ITEM_ID, ISSUE_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, MARKETPLACE_ID, CREDIT_VALUE, SOURCE, ORIG_REV_AMOUNT, CREDIT_VALUE_REMAINING /*, ORDER_ID, FULFILLMENT_TYPE */

SELECT USER_MEMBERSHIP_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, MEMBERSHIP_PLAN_ID, MEMBERSHIP_STATUS, HAS_TRIAL, INCENTIVE_PRODUCT_ID, INCENTIVE_CLAIM_CODE, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, SIGNUP_TYPE, SENT_CLAIM_CODE_EMAIL, EXPECTED_END_DATE FROM booker.AA_USER_MEMBERSHIP_PST where USER_MEMBERSHIP_ID IN(975,976,979,982,977,980,981,983) ORDER BY USER_MEMBERSHIP_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, MEMBERSHIP_PLAN_ID, MEMBERSHIP_STATUS, HAS_TRIAL, INCENTIVE_PRODUCT_ID, INCENTIVE_CLAIM_CODE, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, SIGNUP_TYPE, SENT_CLAIM_CODE_EMAIL, EXPECTED_END_DATE

SELECT MEMB_COMMIT_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, PLAN_ID, MARKETPLACE_ID, CLAIM_CODE_ID, OFFER_TYPE, CONTRACT_LENGTH, CONTRACT_LENGTH_UNIT, START_DATE, UNTIL_DATE, END_DATE, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, SUBS_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, AMZN_CLCD_OFFER_ID FROM booker.AA_MEMBERSHIP_COMMITMENT_PST where MEMB_COMMIT_ID IN(324,276,390) ORDER BY MEMB_COMMIT_ID, CUSTOMER_ID, SUBSCRIPTION_ID, PLAN_ID, MARKETPLACE_ID, CLAIM_CODE_ID, OFFER_TYPE, CONTRACT_LENGTH, CONTRACT_LENGTH_UNIT, START_DATE, UNTIL_DATE, END_DATE, DELETED_FLAG, DATE_UPDATED, SUBS_PLAN_SELECTION_ID, AMZN_CLCD_OFFER_ID
